## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1. Start the application using Aspire AppHost.
2. In `GPOE26.Web`, go to any Create view (e.g. `Event/Create.razor`).
3. Select an image using the new "Upload" option.
4. Verify the file uploads successfully, and the URL field is populated automatically.
5. Save the Event and verify the image displays properly in the lists.
6. Stop the entire Aspire host, restart it, and verify that all data (including the new event and databases in general) are preserved since the Docker volume is now persistent.
